resources.description:
Retrieves a list of server software that the API can process.

### Request parameters
* **`:type`**
  The type of server. Possible values: `standalone` | `proxy`.

### Response type
```js
{
    flavors: [{
        flavor: string, // Name of the flavor.
        manifest: string // Relative link to the manifest for this flavor.
    }, ...]
}
```

Retrieves a manifest of all available versions and builds of a specific flavor.

### Request parameters
* **`:type`**
  The type of server. Possible values: `standalone` | `proxy`.
* **`:flavor`**
  The flaver/variation of software. Possible values can be found by fetching the request above.

### Response type
```js
{
    project: string,
    versions: [{
        version: string,
        builds: [{
            build: number,
            download: string
        }, ...]
    }, ...]
}
```
